attributes.title: #freeadam2020
attributes.review: Ugh! When I tell you I’m soooooooo disappointed with this app! I was so excited when this glorious little square appeared on my home screen. The first disappointment was, it took two months to download and 198.45 GB of data, so I had to delete every other app including pictures of my grandmas pet raccoon who unfortunately passed away last year (r.i.p Mike Rocthburns 😔) When it was ready to open, I had no idea what to expect! When I opened this app, all hell turned lose. My cat immediately started gushing diarrhea all over our white carpet. It was like a stream of sewer water mixed with tapioca pudding, blasting from his poor little butthole. Because of all the diarrhea on our carpet, our roomba vacuum (who is very pregnant at the moment with triplets) started making her way around when she slipped and fell! We don’t know how she’s doing but please send your blessings. I’m bored with writing this so but anyways: black lives matter, bunker boy is diabolical, appalling, and hellacious. Have an amazing day, unless your a Trump supporter 😋💓🧚🏻✨
